
Q1.You have a web app hosted on Azure App Service.

You want to:
	•	Deploy a new version of your app
	•	Test it before going live
	•	Switch to the new version without downtime
You have a web app hosted on Azure App Service.

Options:

A) Auto-scale
B) Deployment slots
C) Azure Monitor
D) Backup and Restore

Answer - B) Deployment slots

Deployment slots in Azure App Service let you:
	•	Deploy new versions to a staging slot
	•	Test safely without affecting production
	•	Swap slots → zero downtime release 


